<br />
<br />SMB1:
<br />1 PLAYER GAME = Mario on controller 1
<br />2 PLAYER GAME = alternating Mario on controller 1 with Luigi-colored Mario on controller 2
<br />
<br />SMB2 (J):
<br />MARIO GAME = Mario on controller 1
<br />LUIGI GAME = Luigi with different physics on controller 1, nothing on controller 2

		

