	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I would start simple:  Hack the existing physics code to make Mario jump like Luigi in SMB2j.  Play SMB2j and look for the variables that change when Luigi jumps (Use a debugger like fceux).  I'm sure both games use the same jumping code but with different parameters.
<br />
<br />If you want to add code to SMB, that's going to be difficult because there's no empty space.  The code will have to be organized and split into several banks with bankswitching code added.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


